      <section eId="sec_7_6_19">
        <num>7-6.19</num>
        <heading>Accounting by and determination of liability of custodian</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_7_6_19__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>A minor who has attained the age of fourteen years, the minor's\nguardian or legal representative, an adult member of the minor's family,\na transferor, or a transferor's legal representative may petition the\ncourt</p>
          </content>
          <paragraph eId="sec_7_6_19__subsec_a__subsec_1">
            <num>(1)</num>
            <content>
              <p>for an accounting by the custodian or the custodian's legal\nrepresentative; or</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_7_6_19__subsec_a__subsec_2">
            <num>(2)</num>
            <content>
              <p>for a determination of responsibility, as between\nthe custodial property and the custodian personally, for claims against\nthe custodial property unless the responsibility has been adjudicated in\nan action under 7-6.17 to which the minor or the minor's legal\nrepresentative was a party.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_7_6_19__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>A successor custodian may petition the court for an accounting by\nthe predecessor custodian.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_7_6_19__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The court, in a proceeding under this part or in any other\nproceeding, may require or permit the custodian or the custodian's legal\nrepresentative to account.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_7_6_19__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>If a custodian is removed under paragraph</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_7_6_19__subsec_f">
          <num>(f)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of 7-6.18, the court\nshall require an accounting and order delivery of the custodial property\nand records to the successor custodian and the execution of all\ninstruments required for transfer of the custodial property.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
